trans-unit.source: Represents the details of a discovery reference without the contents of the referenced document.
trans-unit.target: Representerer detaljene for en discovery referanse uten innholdet i det refererte dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Using the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A> method of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol>, all valid referenced documents and a file containing a map of all save documents can be written to disk.
trans-unit.target: Ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A>-metoden til <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol>, skrives alle gyldig refererte dokumenter og en fil som inneholder en tilordning for alle lagre dokumenter til disken.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A>

trans-unit.source: The file containing a map of all saved documents contains the details of each document as summarized by the properties of DiscoveryClientResult.
trans-unit.target: Filen som inneholder en tilordning for alle lagrede dokumenter inneholder detaljer for hvert dokument som et sammendrag av egenskaper for DiscoveryClientResult.

trans-unit.source: After the referenced documents and the map of the referenced documents have been written to disk using the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A> method, you can invoke the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll%2A> method to read the discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: Når de refererte dokumentene og tilordner refererte dokumenter som er skrevet til disken ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A>metoden, kan du aktivere den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll%2A>metode for å lese discovery-dokumenter.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ReadAll%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.WriteAll%2A>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den klassen og angir de <> *> egenskapen referenceType , <> *> egenskapen url og egenskapen filename .

trans-unit.source: Name of the class representing the type of reference in the discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på klassen som representerer referansetypen i discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.ReferenceTypeName*> property.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.ReferenceTypeName*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.ReferenceTypeName*>

trans-unit.source: URL for the reference.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen for referansen.

trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.Url*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.Url*>

trans-unit.source: Name of the file in which the reference was saved.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på filen som referansen ble lagret.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.Filename*> property.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.Filename*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult.Filename*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the file in which the reference is saved.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på filen der referansen er lagret.

trans-unit.source: The name of the file is the name of the file saved on the local computer based on the contents of the file.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på filen er navnet på filen lagres på den lokale datamaskinen som er basert på innholdet i filen.

trans-unit.source: For instance, if the referenced file is a discovery document, the saved file will have a.disco extension on a Windows operating system.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis filen refereres til en discovery-dokumentet, får den lagrede filen a.disco utvidelsen på en Windows-operativsystem.

trans-unit.source: Name of the file in which the reference is saved.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på filen der referansen er lagret.

trans-unit.source: Name of the class representing the type of reference in the discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på klassen som representerer referansetypen i discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: A reference within a discovery document can contain references to service descriptions, XSD schemas, or other discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: En referanse i discovery-dokumentet kan inneholde referanser til tjenestebeskrivelser av, XSD-skjema eller andre discovery-dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, ReferenceTypeName can have the following values: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>, and <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>.
trans-unit.target: ReferenceTypeName kan derfor ha følgende verdier: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>, og <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> </xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: Name of the class representing the type of a reference.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på klassen som representerer en referansetypen.

trans-unit.source: Default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL for the reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URL-adressen for referansen.

trans-unit.source: The URL can refer to a discovery document, XML Schema Definition (XSD) schema, or a Service Description.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen kan referere til en discovery-dokumentet, XML-skjema definisjon (XSD) schema eller en beskrivelse av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the reference.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen referanse.
